author: Leada Gore | lgore@al.com
title: A Day Without a Woman: What to expect on March 8 International Women's Day protest
text: "A Day Without a Woman," the latest effort by the organizers of January's massive Women's March on Washington, is set for Wednesday. The protest coincides with International Women's Day, a global event that traces its origins to 1909.
